title: [deap loop] HashMap remove
body:

Rust version linux 1.45.2


the fd is RawFd

the code
```
impl<'a> Drop for ListenerToken<'a> {
    fn drop(&mut self) {
        let fd = self.fd;
       self.fd = -1;
            if let Some(key) = {
                let mut lock = self.cm.fds.lock().unwrap();
                lock.used.remove(&fd)
            } {
                info!("{} released", key);
            }
        }
    }
}
```
